<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/MorphologicalCharacteristics> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/MorphologicalCharacteristics> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http:/purl.org/scimin-crm-mwf/core:Characteristics> .
